summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of North and West Sixtieth Street from Eighth Avenue N.W. to Phinney Avenue in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 17178, creating Local Improvement District No. 1615 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
